---
import { SITE_TITLE } from '@/consts'
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro'

const metaTitle = `About | ${SITE_TITLE}`
const metaDescription = 'About'
---

<Layout {metaTitle} {metaDescription}>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
    <h1 class="text-foreground mb-8 text-4xl font-bold">About</h1>

    <div class="max-w-none">
      <p class="mb-6">
        Hi, I'm Jason! I'm a Tech Lead at <a href="https://www.offerzen.com" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">OfferZen</a>
        with a background in full-stack development and education. I'm based in Cape Town, South Africa 🌍
      </p>

      <p class="mb-6">
        I initially started my career in education before moving into IT and finally software development. I spent 6+ years as a full-stack
        developer, mostly working with PHP (Laravel) on the backend and a variety of JavaScript frameworks (React, Svelte, Vue.js) on the
        frontend. I'm currently working as a tech lead, which I find to be the perfect mix of technical and people skills.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-foreground mt-8 mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">What I Do</h2>
      <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li>🎯 Building stuff @ OfferZen</li>
        <li>💻 Tinkering with side projects (mostly with Laravel & React)</li>
        <li>👨‍🏫 Mentoring developers and people looking to break into tech</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">Current Tech Stack</h2>
      <div class="mb-6">
        <pre
          class="bg-muted text-muted-foreground rounded-lg p-4 text-sm"><code>Frontend: Inertia.js (React), Next.js, Astro
Backend: Laravel (PHP), Rails (Ruby)</code></pre>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">I'm Passionate About</h2>
      <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Building high-performing engineering teams</li>
        <li>Making tech education more accessible</li>
        <li>Creating positive impact through technology</li>
        <li>Mentoring junior developers</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">Get in Touch</h2>
      <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li>🔗 <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jasontame-052868106" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">LinkedIn</a></li>
      </ul>

      <p class="">
        I'm passionate about mentoring and coaching junior developers and people looking to break into the industry. I am also always
        looking to contribute to projects that seek to make a positive impact within education, particularly within Southern Africa.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
